id: pmc-otpe
title: Harden npm package metadata and CI release gates
description: "Ensure pm-changelog has complete package metadata, an explicit MIT license, deterministic TypeScript emission, and CI checks that catch release regressions before merge."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 0
