author: codex
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "- LICENSE exists and matches the MIT declaration in package.json.\n- npm scripts expose release:check, audit:prod, and pack:dry-run.\n- CI runs type check, tests, production audit, package dry-run, and changelog check using free GitHub Actions features.\n- TypeScript does not emit dist output when compilation has errors."
