body: "Implementation notes:\n- Add repository license text matching package.json.\n- Add release verification scripts for type-checking, tests, production dependency audit, package dry-run, and changelog freshness.\n- Expand GitHub Actions CI to run the same release gates on push and pull requests.\n- Keep dist tracked because pm package installs from GitHub must work without a build step."
